             was indicted for <rs id="t18220417-33-off176" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220417-33-off176" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220417-33-off176" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220417-33-cd177" type="crimeDate">11th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-33-off176 t18220417-33-cd177"></join>, one handkerchief, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220417-33-victim359" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
                           Buckland
                        <interp inst="t18220417-33-victim359" type="surname" value="Buckland"></interp>
